name: Urbanism Issue 3
description:
ATTENTION: THIS ISSUE IS NOW AVAILABLE AT GRAFF-CITY, OINK INK AND ART PRIMO WEBSITES. FOR COPIES PLEASE LOOK THERE. 

Urbanism issue 3 is a special issue for us, a brand new layout, brand new templates, the best new features and content plus all new book format - glue bound with a spine! 

Featuring Ewokone, Mise and Derek, Sticker Traders, Amazing new photographs from burners to dirty throwups and world panels, Concrete Canvas Sketchbook Review, How & Nosm (TATS crew) over the last 20 years of their metro paintings, Exclusive literature from Jeloe and Oink's new ink colours and staining power reviews!

Do not miss this issue! Grab a copy now for our same great price, they're limited!

name: Urbanism issue 2
description:
Urbanism issue 2 - A5, Full colour, 54 pages, saddle stitched. Features interviews with Eiregata, Nickos, Discoshit, Tizer, Belgiums most recent burning hot trains and tons of unseen photos from walls to sticker combos, also featuring exclusive photography! 

Its a must for any street artist, illustrator, photographer or graffiti writer. 

FREE exclusive sticker packet, whilst they last.
